---
import { contactConfig } from '../../config/contact';
import { buildWhatsAppUrl } from '../../lib/whatsapp';
const talkWhatsappUrl = buildWhatsAppUrl(contactConfig.whatsappNumber, 'Olá! Vim pelo site e quero falar com alguém sobre o registro da minha marca.');
---
<section class="section closing">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cta-card reveal">
      <h2>O nome já é seu. Falta o papel.</h2>
      <p>Leva menos tempo do que você levou para escolher o nome.</p>
      <div class="cta-buttons">
        <a class="button button--secondary" href="#cadastro">
          Quero registrar minha marca
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        </a>
        <a class="button button--dark" href={talkWhatsappUrl} target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Prefiro falar com alguém</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<style>
.closing { padding-bottom: 2.5rem; }
.cta-card { position: relative; overflow: hidden; border-radius: 1.75rem; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1); color: var(--color-white); padding: 3.75rem 3.5rem; text-align: center;
  background: radial-gradient(120% 130% at 85% 20%, rgba(120,70,200,.4), transparent 55%), linear-gradient(120deg, var(--color-navy-950), var(--color-indigo-900) 60%, var(--color-purple-900)); }
.cta-card h2 { color: var(--color-white); font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3.6vw, 2.625rem); font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.08; max-width: 34rem; margin-inline: auto; }
.cta-card p { color: var(--color-on-dark); font-size: 1.06rem; line-height: 1.6; max-width: 26rem; margin: 1.125rem auto 1.875rem; }
.cta-buttons { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: .875rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
@media (max-width: 560px) { .cta-card { padding: 2.25rem 1.375rem; } .cta-buttons { flex-direction: column; } .cta-buttons .button { width: 100%; } }
</style>
